### Troll
***Ability Score Increase.*** Your Constitution score increases by 2.

***Age.***

***Alignment.***

***Creature Type.*** You are a Humanoid.

***Size.*** Your size is Medium.

***Speed.*** Your base walking speed is 30 feet.

***Fast Healing.*** You regain twice as many hit points when taking rests.

***Regeneration.*** You regain 1 lost hit point per character level per hour.


Limited Regeneration
You regain all your Hit Dice on a long rest. Additionally, if you lose a body part, the missing part will regrow and return to full functionality after a passing of time, based on the body part:

Fingers & Toes: 1 week
Hands & Feet: 2 weeks
Arm (to elbow) & Leg (to knee): 4 weeks
Eye: 6 weeks
Arm (to shoulder) & Leg (to hip): 8 weeks

